<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="author" content="PandaTool">
    <meta name="copyright" content="PandaTool https://pandatool.org">
    <!-- Built by PandaTool | https://pandatool.org | https://t.me/pandatool -->
    <title>TRON DEX - Nile Testnet | PandaTool</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tronweb@5.3.0/dist/TronWeb.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff0066;
            --secondary: #00d4ff;
            --accent: #ffcc00;
            --bg-dark: #0a0e27;
            --bg-card: #161b33;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #8a92b2;
            --border: #2d3454;
            --success: #00ff88;
            --error: #ff3366;
            --glow: rgba(255, 0, 102, 0.5);
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255,0,102,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(0,212,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 20%, rgba(255,204,0,0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
            animation: gradientShift 15s ease infinite;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        @keyframes gradientShift { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:.8;transform:scale(1.1)} }
        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg,var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            opacity: 0.1; z-index: -1;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        header {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: 2px; animation: logoGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes logoGlow { 0%,100%{filter:brightness(1)} 50%{filter:brightness(1.3)} }
        .network-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,0,102,.2),rgba(0,212,255,.2));
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary); padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,212,255,.3);
        }
        .network-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; background: var(--success); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1} 50%{transform:scale(1.2);opacity:.7} }
        .wallet-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),#cc0052);
            border: none; padding: 14px 30px; border-radius: 12px; color: white;
            font-family: 'Orbitron',sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255,0,102,.4);
        }
        .wallet-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(255,0,102,.6); }
        .main-content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; }
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card); border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 32px; position: relative; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255,0,102,.2); }
        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Orbitron',sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 22px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--text-primary),var(--text-secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .tabs {
            display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 22px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.02); padding: 5px; border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border); flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .tab {
            flex: 1; padding: 9px 12px; border: none; background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
            font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all .3s ease; min-width: 65px; white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .tab.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary)); color: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,0,102,.3); }
        .tab:hover:not(.active) { background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); color: var(--text-primary); }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .input-label { display: block; margin-bottom: 7px; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .token-address-input {
            width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 2px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-primary); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size: 11px;
            outline: none; padding: 11px 13px; border-radius: 11px; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .token-address-input:focus { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,0,102,.2); }
        .token-address-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-secondary); opacity: .4; font-size: 10px; }
        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 13px; padding: 13px; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .input-wrapper:focus-within { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,0,102,.2); }
        .token-input {
            width: 100%; background: transparent; border: none; color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;
            outline: none; padding-right: 110px;
        }
        .token-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-secondary); opacity: .5; }
        .token-symbol-display {
            position: absolute; right: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,0,102,.2),rgba(0,212,255,.2));
            border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-primary);
            padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 9px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
            font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; pointer-events: none;
        }
        .query-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--secondary),#0099cc); border: none;
            padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 8px; color: white;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px;
            cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease; margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .query-btn:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,212,255,.4); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .query-btn:disabled { opacity: .5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
        .balance { margin-top: 7px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .max-btn {
            background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--secondary); color: var(--secondary);
            padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .max-btn:hover { background: var(--secondary); color: var(--bg-dark); }
        .swap-arrow { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 10px 0; }
        .swap-arrow-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary));
            border: 3px solid var(--bg-card); width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%;
            color: white; font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,0,102,.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .swap-arrow-btn:hover { transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.1); box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(255,0,102,.6); }
        .info-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 13px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 18px; }
        .info-row {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            padding: 7px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05); word-break: break-all;
        }
        .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .info-label { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; text-align: right; }
        .action-btn {
            width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary));
            border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 13px; color: white;
            font-family: 'Orbitron',sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer; margin-top: 18px; transition: all .3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(255,0,102,.4); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .action-btn::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.3),transparent);
            transition: left .5s ease;
        }
        .action-btn:hover::before { left: 100%; }
        .action-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 35px rgba(255,0,102,.6); }
        .action-btn:disabled { opacity: .5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
        .action-btn.danger-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4466,#cc0033); }
        .settings { margin-top: 18px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 13px; }
        .settings-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 12px; }
        .slippage-options { display: flex; gap: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .slippage-btn {
            flex: 1; padding: 7px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; min-width: 45px;
        }
        .slippage-btn.active { background: var(--primary); color: white; border-color: var(--primary); }
        .slippage-btn:hover:not(.active) { border-color: var(--primary); background: rgba(255,0,102,.1); }
        .slippage-custom-input {
            flex: 1; min-width: 65px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-primary); padding: 7px; border-radius: 7px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; outline: none; text-align: center;
        }
        .slippage-custom-input:focus { border-color: var(--primary); }
        .status-message { margin-top: 13px; padding: 13px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; animation: slideIn .3s ease; }
        @keyframes slideIn { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-8px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
        .status-success { background: rgba(0,255,136,.1); border: 1px solid var(--success); color: var(--success); }
        .status-error   { background: rgba(255,51,102,.1); border: 1px solid var(--error); color: var(--error); }
        .status-info    { background: rgba(0,212,255,.1);  border: 1px solid var(--secondary); color: var(--secondary); }
        .status-warning { background: rgba(255,204,0,.1);  border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
        .spinner { display: inline-block; width: 13px; height: 13px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); border-top-color: white; border-radius: 50%; animation: spin .8s linear infinite; margin-right: 7px; }
        @keyframes spin { to{transform:rotate(360deg)} }
        .preset-tokens { display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 5px; }
        .preset-token-btn {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding: 4px 9px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size: 10px;
            cursor: pointer; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .preset-token-btn:hover { border-color: var(--secondary); color: var(--secondary); background: rgba(0,212,255,.05); }
        /* Remove liquidity */
        .percent-display { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); text-align: center; margin: 12px 0; }
        .percent-slider { width: 100%; accent-color: var(--primary); cursor: pointer; margin: 8px 0; height: 6px; }
        .quick-pcts { display: flex; gap: 7px; margin: 10px 0; }
        .quick-pct-btn {
            flex: 1; padding: 7px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 11px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-weight: 600; transition: all .3s ease;
        }
        .quick-pct-btn:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); background: rgba(255,0,102,.1); }
        .brand-tag{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary);letter-spacing:.5px;margin-top:4px;}
        .brand-link{color:var(--secondary);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;transition:color .2s;}
        .brand-link:hover{color:var(--primary);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,0,102,.5);}
        .dex-footer{text-align:center;padding:22px 0 16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:30px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
        .footer-sep{color:var(--border);}
        @media(max-width:1024px){.main-content{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
        @media(max-width:768px){.logo{font-size:22px} header{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start} .card{padding:18px}}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:7px}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg-dark)}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary));border-radius:6px}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <header>
        <div class="logo">TRON DEX</div>
        <div class="brand-tag">Powered by <a href="https://pandatool.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="brand-link">🐼 PandaTool</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="https://t.me/pandatool" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="brand-link">✈️ Telegram</a></div>
        <div class="network-badge">
            <div class="network-dot"></div>
            <span>Nile Testnet</span>
        </div>
        <button class="wallet-btn" id="connectWallet">🔌 连接钱包</button>
    </header>

    <div class="main-content">
        <!-- ===== LEFT CARD ===== -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="card-title">💰 交易面板</h2>
            <div class="tabs">
                <button class="tab active" data-tab="swap">🔄 兑换</button>
                <button class="tab" data-tab="addLiquidity">➕ 添加流动性</button>
                <button class="tab" data-tab="removeLiquidity">➖ 移除流动性</button>
            </div>

            <!-- SWAP -->
            <div id="swapPanel">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">📥 支付 (From)</label>
                    <input type="text" class="token-address-input" id="fromTokenAddress"
                        placeholder="代币合约地址，TRX 请直接输入 TRX"
                        value="TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf">
                    <div class="preset-tokens">
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setFromToken('TRX')">🔥 TRX</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setFromToken('TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf')">💵 USDT</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setFromToken('TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz')">💲 USDC</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setFromToken('TFT7sNiNDGZcqL7z7dwXUPpxrx1Ewk8iGL')">🪙 USDD</button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="query-btn" id="queryFromBtn" style="width:100%">🔍 查询代币信息</button>
                    <div class="input-wrapper" style="margin-top:7px">
                        <input type="number" class="token-input" id="fromAmount" placeholder="0.0" step="any">
                        <span class="token-symbol-display" id="fromSymbol">---</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="balance">
                        <span>💰 余额: <span id="fromBalance">0.0000</span> <span id="fromBalanceSymbol"></span></span>
                        <button class="max-btn" id="maxBtn">MAX</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="swap-arrow">
                    <button class="swap-arrow-btn" id="swapTokens" title="切换方向">⇅</button>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">📤 接收 (To)</label>
                    <input type="text" class="token-address-input" id="toTokenAddress"
                        placeholder="代币合约地址，TRX 请直接输入 TRX"
                        value="TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz">
                    <div class="preset-tokens">
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setToToken('TRX')">🔥 TRX</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setToToken('TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf')">💵 USDT</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setToToken('TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz')">💲 USDC</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setToToken('TFT7sNiNDGZcqL7z7dwXUPpxrx1Ewk8iGL')">🪙 USDD</button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="query-btn" id="queryToBtn" style="width:100%">🔍 查询代币信息</button>
                    <div class="input-wrapper" style="margin-top:7px">
                        <input type="number" class="token-input" id="toAmount" placeholder="0.0" readonly>
                        <span class="token-symbol-display" id="toSymbol">---</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="balance">
                        <span>💰 余额: <span id="toBalance">0.0000</span> <span id="toBalanceSymbol"></span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top:10px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
                    🔄 SunSwap V2 Router
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">📊 兑换率</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="rate">-</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">📦 最少收到 (含滑点)</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="minReceived">-</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">📉 价格影响</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="priceImpact">-</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="action-btn" id="swapBtn">💱 执行兑换 Swap</button>
            </div>

            <!-- ADD LIQUIDITY -->
            <div id="addLiquidityPanel" style="display:none">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">🪙 Token A</label>
                    <input type="text" class="token-address-input" id="tokenAAddress"
                        placeholder="Token A 地址" value="TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf">
                    <div class="preset-tokens">
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenA('TRX')">🔥 TRX</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenA('TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf')">💵 USDT</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenA('TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz')">💲 USDC</button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="query-btn" id="queryTokenABtn" style="width:100%">🔍 查询</button>
                    <div class="input-wrapper" style="margin-top:7px">
                        <input type="number" class="token-input" id="tokenAAmount" placeholder="0.0" step="any">
                        <span class="token-symbol-display" id="tokenASymbol">---</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="balance"><span>💰 余额: <span id="tokenABalance">0.0000</span></span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swap-arrow"><span style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:22px;text-align:center;display:block">➕</span></div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="input-label">🪙 Token B</label>
                    <input type="text" class="token-address-input" id="tokenBAddress"
                        placeholder="Token B 地址" value="TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz">
                    <div class="preset-tokens">
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenB('TRX')">🔥 TRX</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenB('TXYZopYRdj2D9XRtbG411XZZ3kM5VkAeBf')">💵 USDT</button>
                        <button class="preset-token-btn" onclick="setLiquidityTokenB('TEMVynQpntMqkPxP6wXTW2K7e4sM3cRmWz')">💲 USDC</button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="query-btn" id="queryTokenBBtn" style="width:100%">🔍 查询</button>
                    <div class="input-wrapper" style="margin-top:7px">
                        <input type="number" class="token-input" id="tokenBAmount" placeholder="0.0" step="any">
                        <span class="token-symbol-display" id="tokenBSymbol">---</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="balance"><span>💰 余额: <span id="tokenBBalance">0.0000</span></span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-box">
                    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">🏊 池子状态</span><span class="info-value" id="poolStatus">查询代币后自动检测</span></div>
                    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">📊 当前比例</span><span class="info-value" id="poolRatio">-</span></div>
                    <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">📊 池子份额</span><span class="info-value" id="poolShare">0%</span></div>
                </div>
                <button class="action-btn" id="addLiquidityBtn">💧 添加流动性</button>
            </div>

